    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. This example has been meticulously maintained with a focus on preventative measures, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a limited-slip differential that maintains excellent power distribution. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein dampers and poly-bushings for sharpened turn-in and reduced body roll. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a driver's car, the internal combustion health and drivetrain tolerances remain within tight enthusiast standards.",
      "price": 34500.0,
